init_text: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You can see in detail the events that will occur in your next life, but you're unable to interact with the movie.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You married a man you didn't love, but who was a decent person and an excellent king.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You watched your movie life and learned that you would soon be reincarnated as a man in Japan.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Your movie ended and you were forced to leave the theatre.
